# The differences within an organization help make it strong

[See plans for business](https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/business#compareProductsRegion) [See plans for enterprise](https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/enterprise/microsoft365-plans-and-pricing)

